Package: sentry.sdk
Title: Rust-Powered Sentry SDK Bindings for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Adam", "Smielewski", , "adam.smielewski@finccam.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides minimal R bindings to the Sentry Rust SDK for
    initializing a client, capturing messages, and creating transactions
    and spans with inbound distributed tracing support.
